### User Auth - Tenant Template Admin APIs
### Required scope: SCOPE_TENANT_ROLE_ASSIGN

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@tenantAccessToken = 15b00968-4eab-457b-921f-9c0a28261158
@tenantId = b32094dc-734c-4063-b289-a5882b061b72
@tenantTemplateCode = TEMPLATE_TENANT_CUSTOM_WORK
@platformTemplateCode = TEMPLATE_BRAND_WORK
@roleCode = TENANT_OPERATOR
@permissionCode = BRAND_RELEASE

### 1) Create tenant template
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/tenants/{{tenantId}}/permission-templates
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "{{tenantTemplateCode}}",
  "name": "Tenant Custom Work",
  "description": "Tenant specific operator template"
}

### 2) List visible templates (global + tenant)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/tenants/{{tenantId}}/permission-templates
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantAccessToken}}

### 3) Get tenant-visible template detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/tenants/{{tenantId}}/permission-templates/{{tenantTemplateCode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantAccessToken}}

### 4) Update tenant template
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/tenants/{{tenantId}}/permission-templates/{{tenantTemplateCode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Tenant Custom Work v2",
  "description": "Updated by tenant admin",
  "enabled": true
}

### 5) Replace tenant template permissions
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/tenants/{{tenantId}}/permission-templates/{{tenantTemplateCode}}/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "permissionCodes": ["BRAND_RELEASE"]
}

### 6) Add tenant template permissions
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/tenants/{{tenantId}}/permission-templates/{{tenantTemplateCode}}/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "permissionCodes": ["BRAND_RELEASE"]
}

### 7) Remove tenant template permission
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/tenants/{{tenantId}}/permission-templates/{{tenantTemplateCode}}/permissions/{{permissionCode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantAccessToken}}

### 8) Bind template to tenant role
## role은 3개 OPERATOR,STAFF, ADMIN
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/tenants/{{tenantId}}/role-templates
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "roleCode": "{{roleCode}}",
  "templateCode": "{{platformTemplateCode}}"
}

### 9) List tenant role-template bindings
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/tenants/{{tenantId}}/role-templates
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantAccessToken}}

### 10) Unbind template from tenant role
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/tenants/{{tenantId}}/role-templates/{{roleCode}}/{{platformTemplateCode}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantAccessToken}}
